Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper analyzes a large-scale online marketplace and its social and economic impact.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the societal and regulatory issues surrounding Airbnb.
- cs.CS (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possible category as the paper uses computational methods to analyze the data set.
- cs.SD (Software Development) is a possible category as the paper may be of interest to developers working on similar online marketplaces.
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is a possible category as the paper analyzes the behavior of hosts and guests on Airbnb.
